<div class="wrapper has-background-white case-studies">
<div class="container columns is-multiline is-variable is-6-desktop is-8-widescreen">
<div class="column is-full">
<h2 class="title has-text-navy-black py-5">Real-world users</h2>
</div>
<div class="column is-one-third">
<a href="https://buoyant.io/case-studies/adidas/" target="_blank" class="card-link">
<div class="card">
<header class="card-header">
<figure class="image">
<img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZwogIHdpZHRoPSIyNDIiCiAgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMjIiCiAgZmlsbD0ibm9uZSIKICB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPgo8L3N2Zz4=" data-src="/uploads/logos/blue/adidas.png" class="lazyload " alt="Adidas" />
</figure>
</header>
<div class="card-content">
<div class="content">
&#34;All our observability gaps were closed, ...we saw a reduction in failed requests, and experienced cost reduction due to better performance.&#34;
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="column is-one-third">
<a href="https://buoyant.io/case-studies/xbox/" target="_blank" class="card-link">
<div class="card">
<header class="card-header">
<figure class="image">
<img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZwogIHdpZHRoPSIyNDIiCiAgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMjIiCiAgZmlsbD0ibm9uZSIKICB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPgo8L3N2Zz4=" data-src="/uploads/logos/blue/xbox.png" class="lazyload " alt="Xbox" />
</figure>
</header>
<div class="card-content">
<div class="content">
&#34;We have offloaded the time and effort needed to develop and maintain the in-house mTLS solution, saving valuable engineering hours...&#34;
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="column is-one-third">
<a href="https://buoyant.io/case-studies/schenker/" target="_blank" class="card-link">
<div class="card">
<header class="card-header">
<figure class="image">
<img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZwogIHdpZHRoPSIyNDIiCiAgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMjIiCiAgZmlsbD0ibm9uZSIKICB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPgo8L3N2Zz4=" data-src="/uploads/logos/blue/db-schenker.png" class="lazyload " alt="DB Schenker" />
</figure>
</header>
<div class="card-content">
<div class="content">
&#34;Linkerd started as our cloud migration tool and ended up being our service mesh of choice.&#34;
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
</div>
</div>
